   Ruvalcaba cut off Deputy Police Chief Tommy Tunson in mid-sentence
while he was protesting an unusual move forcing all officers,
including police brass, to wear uniforms.

   The list of police officers under "disciplinary investigation" by
the Colombian inspector-general's office includes Gen. Gustavo Socha,
who resigned last month as chief of the counter-narcotics police;
Col. Yadira Angelica Rivera, in charge of international relations;
Col. Carlos Julio Rivera; chief of police aviation; and Col. Climaco
Antonio Torres, chief of drug interdiction.

   In the 79th minute, Klose made it 2-0 with a header on a cross
from Ballack. Klose, who scored a hat trick against Saudi Arabia,
leads the tournament with five goals.
